## ğŸ—‚ï¸ Understanding Repositories (Repos)
- **Repos** = Repositories â€” storage locations for software packages.
- Contain URLs pointing to package sources (online mirrors or local servers).
- Config files stored in:  
  `/etc/yum.repos.d/`  
